WEBVTT

00:05:29.363 --> 00:05:33.025
politically closed,
and morally illegitimate.

00:05:33.049 --> 00:05:36.235
Well, the assumptions are wrong.

00:05:36.259 --> 00:05:38.445
The opposites are true.

00:05:38.469 --> 00:05:41.783
Adaptability, meritocracy, and legitimacy

00:05:41.807 --> 00:05:43.717
are the three defining characteristics

00:05:43.741 --> 00:05:46.088
of China's one-party system.

00:05:46.112 --> 00:05:48.160
Now, most political
scientists will tell us

00:05:48.184 --> 00:05:51.345
that a one-party system
is inherently incapable

00:05:51.369 --> 00:05:53.273
of self-correction.

00:05:53.297 --> 00:05:55.591
It won't last long
because it cannot adapt.

00:05:55.615 --> 00:05:57.389
Now here are the facts.

00:05:57.413 --> 00:06:00.949
